            "id": 6408828,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 台半(5425)股價拉至漲停，漲停價58.6元，成交4,678張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台半(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5425:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5425\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5425-TW</a>)07日11:13上漲5.3元，股價漲停報58.6元，委買5,000張、委賣246,000張，成交4,678張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為整流器之生產製造．銷售及進出口業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台半(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5425:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5425\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5425-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌2.56%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.78%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-4,927 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-4,092 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-2 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-833 張</li> <li>融資增減：+100 張</li> <li>融券增減：-11 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
