            "id": 6408821,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 萊德光電-KY(7717)股價拉至漲停，漲停價804.0元，成交980張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>萊德光電-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7717:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7717\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7717-TW</a>)07日11:01上漲73元，股價漲停報804.0元，委買65,000張，成交980張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為光纖通訊被動元件、光纖雷射被動元件及智慧照明等。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>萊德光電-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:7717:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/7717\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">7717-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌0.27%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.78%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-233 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-214 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-19 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
